lines.text: C6-39 Abraham Welsh Road North York Ontario MOM 0B7
Thank you for seeing this pleasant 29 year old lady who presents with Oligomenorrhoea of about 4-5 mentrual period in a
year. Blood work showed raised Testosterone but normal Prolactin, FSH and LA levels. Ultrasound of the pelvis was
normal. I will be grateful for your kind assessment and management.
Background history of neonatal jaundice with no apparent cause of this during neonatal period. Developed learning disability,
poor motor function and hearing impairment since then.
No Known Drug Allergies Custom Allergy
